ely as if grasping for something unseen, illuminated by dramatic chiaroscuro lighting that casts deep, menacing shadows across its knuckles; beside it, a young female roe deer stands alert in tall, golden-brown grass, her reddish-brown fur shimmering faintly under diffused, warm dawn light, ears perked, eyes watchful and still, partially concealed by vegetation, evoking quiet tension and wild grace; the scene unfolds in a lush, rain-drenched forest beside a river where a panther crawls alongside her cub in distress, both clinging to gnarled tree bark slick with water droplets, surrounded by vibrant, surreal colored flowers blooming defiantly among the moss and roots, captured in a 35mm lens with grainy texture, vintage Kodachrome Lomography aesthetic, vignette framing, volumetric lighting casting ethereal beams through the canopy, rendered with Octane’s hyper-detailed realism, blending whimsical imagination with heartwarming intimacy, all within a color palette that balances the monochrome horror of the hand with the warm, earthy tones of the deer and the vivid, saturated life of the flora, evoking a world where the supernatural and the natural collide in a breathtaking, emotionally resonant tableau."]},{"id":83,"type":"String","pos":[-130,910],"size":[400,200],"flags":{},"order":3,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"String","name":"String","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"String"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"STRING","name":"STRING","type":"STRING","links":[183]}],"title":"Prompt to enhance","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyliterals","ver":"bdddb08ca82d90d75d97b1d437a652e0284a32ac","Node name for S&R":"String","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"}},"widgets_values":["hyper realistic photograph,a image of a panther next to her cub in distress crawling on a tree bark in the river,water droplets,colored flowers,35mm photo,grainy,vignette,vintage,Kodachrome,Lomography,highly detailed,octane render,highl